metadata.name: The Enlightened
metadata.description: A Dark Mage amidst a ritual to reach his past, present and future. Inside the caves of Kratu, the Enlightened one resides inside peacefully away from the war torn lands outside, the key to saving all of existing life. Destructive forces search the lands to destroy every dark mage left in the universe, only too fail. All Dark Mages left alive cast a spell to save all humanity.
